      "role": "user",
      "content": "urgent care is so expensive though and the wait is probably hours... honestly it's not even that painful, just a bit uncomfortable. if i just use some of those preservative-free drops and maybe a warm compress every few hours, can't it just clear up on its own? i really don't want to deal with a doctor if it's just minor irritation.",
